{
  "stem": "23350.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And from there, in the afternoon, I went to a Jewish school which was called [NON-ENGLISH] for learning religious-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] you know, to pray in Hebrew and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The school was like in a private house, just for certain children which was held there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a very big school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was a very, very good school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The little bit which I know is from Yiddish [? guide ?] is all which I learned in those years at home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At home in the school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always got together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we learned also all the nice songs-- the Israeli songs.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] You know, and we learned the Hatikvah and all these different-- we learned to dance the Horah, all the children.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And every time we had a play, whenever it was before a holiday, they made a play up, where we all tried to act in it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was for Purim.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had the Purim story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all the different festivals which we had.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was really very, very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a child, I had it really good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I've got very good memories as a child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The orientation of the school was purely a religious school-- mainly a religious school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course it was also Zionist, because we all were hoping one day to be in Israel and to get to know the country, and maybe one day to live there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as small children, as we were in my age, we mainly were taught to read and write Yiddish and daven in Hebrew, pray.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we celebrated the festivals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were wonderful, the festivals at home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was such a community.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a small town, but many came to Friday night.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
